 class=\"nu0\">15px</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">0</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">padding</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">5px</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">background</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">#f7f5ed</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">border</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">1px</span><span class=\"\"> solid </span><span class=\"nu0\">#cccabc</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">border-radius</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">2px</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">width</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> calc</span><span class=\"br0\">(</span><span class=\"nu0\">100%</span><span class=\"\"> - </span><span class=\"nu0\">15px</span><span class=\"br0\">)</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">max-width</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">400px</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"br0\">}</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"kw1\">footer </span><span class=\"br0\">{</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">width</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">100%</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">display</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> inline-block</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"br0\">}</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"kw1\">footer .menu </span><span class=\"br0\">{</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">float</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> none</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">text-align</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> center</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">margin-top</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">10px</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"br0\">}</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"kw1\">footer .menu li a </span><span class=\"br0\">{</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">padding</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">6px</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span class=\"\">    </span><span class=\"kw3\">margin</span><span class=\"sy0\">:</span><span class=\"\"> </span><span class=\"nu0\">6px</span><span class=\"sy0\">;</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" even\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"br0\">}</span><span class=\"\"></span></li><li class=\" odd\"><span clas